          "activation_name": "Dispatch Messenger",
          "activation_time": "1 minute",
          "effect": "The ring casts *animal messenger* to your specification. The animal is a magical creature that springs from the ring, and its appearance suits the iconography or heraldry of the leader or organization represented by the ring.",
